9
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:01,040
Don't overthink it.

10
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,400
Get a good night's sleep.

11
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:15,039
No more phone at night.

12
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:20,159
Good night.

13
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,159
[Good night.]

14
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:40,000
Where does he usually sleep?

15
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,919
Anyway, the sheets are new.

16
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:50,319
Just pretend I'm in a hotel.

17
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:06,280
Hello?

18
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,319
Hello?

19
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,360
Ruan Yu, are you okay?

20
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,560
I'm fine.

21
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:15,280
You... you didn't reply.

22
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,960
I was worried.

23
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,680
Glad you're okay.

24
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,000
That's good.

25
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,439
Sorry,

26
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,840
