31
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:36,360
No,
he went to the hotel.

32
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,719
Are you looking for Lawyer Xu
for something?

33
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:45,560
No,

34
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,840
I just thought of

35
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,039
a legal question

36
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:49,840
I wanted to ask him.

37
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,879
It's fine if he's not here.
It's fine.

38
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:52,759
I have his WeChat.

39
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:55,039
If you have any questions,

40
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,240
I can send him a message
and ask.

41
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,479
No need.

42
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,439
No need.

43
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,000
Get some rest.

44
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,080
Take care.

45
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:03,159
Bye.

46
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:20,600
Lawyer Xu,

47
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,519
I'll cover your hotel bill tonight.

48
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:24,759
No need for that.

49
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:26,079
Get some rest.

50
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:32,720
I'll be up late,

51
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,120
