52
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:41,279
Good night.

53
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:44,839
[Xu Huaisong]

54
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,720
[actually says good night to someone?]

55
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:49,639
[Good night.]

56
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:53,319
[Sleep tight.]

57
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,720
[His instant reply]

58
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,839
