59
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,720
[who never lets a girl end a conversation]

60
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,879
[in a novel.]

61
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,600
[Is this aloof guy]

62
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,720
