76
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,680
It's nothing serious.

77
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,360
Just sit on the couch.

78
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:12,720
Okay.

79
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:23,560
Come on.

80
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,160
