do you have any other discomfort?

87
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,600
My throat hurts a bit.

88
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,279
I feel a bit cold.

89
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,319
That's all.

90
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:50,519
Come on.

91
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,560
Cover yourself with a blanket.

92
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,279
Thank you.

93
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,519
I'll get you some hot water.

94
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,639
Here.

95
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,639
Thank you.

96
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,720
Take some fever-reducing medicine.

97
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:33,720
Here.

98
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,120
Drink more water.

99
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,559
I'll make you some medicine.

100
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:24,039
Ruan Yu.

101
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,360
Ruan Yu.

102
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,200
Take the medicine first.

103
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,600
Come on, wake up.

104
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,840
Take the medicine.

105
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:12,679
Ruan Yu.

106
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:16,080
Come on.

107
00:10:16,799 --> 00:10:17,600
Take the medicine first.

108
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:22,960
Come on.

109
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,720
Take another sip.

110
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,360
