111
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:03,919
Is that okay?

112
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,360
What kind of love potion?

113
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,720
Don't talk nonsense.

114
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,120
I've already

115
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:30,279
[for a long time.]

116
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,279
[Could you]

117
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,480
[fall in love with me again?]

118
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,960
Where are my shoes?

119
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:50,960
Morning, Lawyer Xu.

120
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:52,360
You're up.

121
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,000
Why aren't you wearing shoes?

122
00:15:04,039 --> 00:15:05,200
I... I couldn't find

123
00:15:05,399 --> 00:15:06,279
