124
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:08,440
Wait a moment.

125
00:15:17,519 --> 00:15:19,159
The slippers are by the sofa.

126
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:20,720
So yesterday was...

127
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,320
Put on your shoes first.

128
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:26,559
Thank you, Lawyer Xu.

129
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,399
Thank you for

130
00:15:29,799 --> 00:15:30,960
carrying me in yesterday.

131
00:15:31,519 --> 00:15:32,559
You are a writer.

132
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,720
You know how to use words.

133
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,000
You're welcome.

134
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:39,399
Take your temperature again.

135
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,240
Sit.

136
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:04,440
Lawyer Xu, this is...

137
00:16:05,759 --> 00:16:06,399
The research report

138
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:07,759
