139
00:16:11,399 --> 00:16:11,919
Do you believe it?

140
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,559
I'll go wash up first.

141
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:20,480
Okay.

142
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,279
