146
00:16:46,919 --> 00:16:47,840
I want to rent a house
for a transition.

147
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,080
Last night,

148
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:54,240
weren't you still living comfortably

149
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,159
at Xu Huaisong's place?

150
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,679
Are you worried about

151
00:16:56,679 --> 00:16:57,720
