152
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,720
My dear friend, please help me.

153
00:17:02,919 --> 00:17:04,359
Alright, I'll help you.

154
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,440
I'll let you know if I find anything.

155
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,319
Chuan.

156
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,279
Are you busy?

157
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:19,359
Yeah, I'm busy with product selection.

158
00:17:20,519 --> 00:17:22,200
You've been looking at your phone a lot.

159
00:17:22,559 --> 00:17:23,920
Is your shoulder uncomfortable?

160
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,400
And your neck was sore yesterday.

161
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:29,720
Chuan.

162
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:33,079
lend me your ID card.

163
00:17:34,599 --> 00:17:36,039
What do you need it for?

164
00:17:38,759 --> 00:17:42,279
To get our marriage certificate, of course.

165
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,279
Haven't you heard?

166
00:17:47,279 --> 00:17:48,279
You can get it

167
00:17:48,279 --> 00:17:49,640
