168
00:17:54,759 --> 00:17:55,720
Go get it.

169
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,640
Alright, I'll get it for you.

170
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,880
Hurry up.

171
00:18:12,559 --> 00:18:13,920
Hurry, give it to me.

172
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:22,440
Hello?
[Hello,]

173
00:18:23,279 --> 00:18:24,839
[Is this Mr. Zhang Chuan?]

174
00:18:25,279 --> 00:18:25,960
Yes, who's this?

175
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,519
[Hello, Mr. Zhang.]

176
00:18:27,839 --> 00:18:29,240
[This is the front desk of Dacheng Hotel.]

177
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:31,039
[You haven't checked out]

178
00:18:31,039 --> 00:18:31,920
[from room 602 yet.]

179
00:18:34,599 --> 00:18:35,480
I'm not buying a house.

180
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,720
Too many scam calls.

181
00:18:40,039 --> 00:18:41,160
Yeah, there are

182
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,240
