183
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,680
You should download an anti-fraud app.

184
00:18:45,319 --> 00:18:46,279
Alright, I'm heading to work.

185
00:18:47,279 --> 00:18:48,119
Bye.

186
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:53,839
[Miss Shen,]

187
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:55,440
[can you come to inspect the car this afternoon?]

188
00:19:21,319 --> 00:19:21,880
Hello, honey.
Where are you?

189
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,279
I just finished showering

190
00:19:24,599 --> 00:19:25,880
and getting ready to go to the office.

191
00:19:26,519 --> 00:19:28,200
The hotel front desk

192
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,160
