193
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,240
saying you haven't checked out.

194
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,960
I'm worried something happened to you.

195
00:19:32,319 --> 00:19:34,200
I'm fine. See you at the office in a bit.

196
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:35,799
See you later.

197
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:42,680
Hello?
[Hello.]

198
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:45,160
[Is this Mr. Zhang Chuan?]

199
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,200
Yes, who's this?

200
00:19:46,799 --> 00:19:47,720
[Hello, Mr. Zhang.]

201
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,359
[This is the front desk of Dacheng Hotel.]

202
00:19:49,839 --> 00:19:51,240
[You haven't checked out]

203
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,000
[from Room 602 yet.]

204
00:19:53,519 --> 00:19:54,319
I'm not buying a house.

205
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,720
Too many scams.

206
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:24,319
Last night,

207
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:37,680
[did you wake up?]

208
00:20:38,759 --> 00:20:39,720
[How's your stay]
[at Lawyer Xu's?]

209
00:20:42,279 --> 00:20:43,039
Lawyer Xu.

210
00:20:43,119 --> 00:20:44,079
I'll check my WeChat.

211
00:20:49,799 --> 00:20:50,519
I'm doing well.
Don't worry.

212
00:20:52,079 --> 00:20:52,720
As for the legal issue

213
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:54,519
you mentioned yesterday,

214
00:20:54,519 --> 00:20:55,319
is it serious?

215
00:20:55,759 --> 00:20:56,960
I'll ask for you.

216
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,920
No need, it's already been resolved.

217
00:21:05,759 --> 00:21:07,519
What are your plans for today?

218
00:21:09,319 --> 00:21:10,400
I'm going to look for an apartment.

219
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:12,759
Are you thinking of moving?

220
00:21:13,319 --> 00:21:15,240
Yeah, I don't know when

221
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,240
Cen Sisi's case
will be completely resolved.

222
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,480
I shouldn't keep

223
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:19,799
bothering Lawyer Xu.

224
00:21:20,039 --> 00:21:20,799
So I think
it would be more convenient

225
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:22,359
to move to another apartment.
Leave it to me.

226
00:21:23,559 --> 00:21:24,240
I'll help you find a new place.

227
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,519
I'll get it done for you within a day.

228
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,440
No need to rush.

229
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:33,519
You...

230
00:21:34,839 --> 00:21:36,000
You're with Lawyer Xu.

231
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:48,839
Let's go eat first.

232
00:21:49,079 --> 00:21:49,640
It's getting cold.

233
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,799
The custard buns are still warm.

234
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:15,160
Come on, try some.

235
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:18,240
No need.

236
00:22:21,559 --> 00:22:22,759
I'm fine, I'll do it myself.

237
00:22:29,359 --> 00:22:30,400
Why are you blushing?

238
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:31,880
Are you having a fever again?

239
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,240
You have a fever?

240
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:44,480
No, no.

241
00:22:44,839 --> 00:22:45,640
I'm fine today
after what happened yesterday.

242
00:22:52,079 --> 00:22:53,319
Have you been to the hospital?

243
00:22:53,599 --> 00:22:54,240
I'll take you there.

244
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:58,480
No need.

245
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,720
You heard her. No need.

246
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:03,599
Don't be so polite to me.

247
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:04,799
I'm not.

248
00:23:05,119 --> 00:23:06,640
I just feel almost well.

249
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,240
Take your time.

250
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:11,359
Have some milk.

251
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:43,680
You can take it home.

252
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,160
Thanks.
Okay.

253
00:23:52,359 --> 00:23:52,720
Come on.

254
00:23:54,279 --> 00:23:55,039
Do you think

255
00:23:55,519 --> 00:23:56,799
