258
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:05,359
Monthly quiz again?

259
00:24:06,359 --> 00:24:07,680
Today is gift exchange day.

260
00:24:08,279 --> 00:24:08,920
What did you give
to the Ministry of Culture and Entertainment?

261
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:14,680
Don't hide it. I know it all.

262
00:24:15,759 --> 00:24:16,559
What do you know?

263
00:24:17,039 --> 00:24:18,039
I know your little tricks.
You can't hide it from me.

264
00:24:19,799 --> 00:24:20,400
Give it to me.

265
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:22,640
Give what?

266
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,279
Come on. Let's go to eat.

267
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,960
I'm telling you.

268
00:24:28,319 --> 00:24:29,920
As friends,

269
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,319
what don't I know about you?

270
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,640
We are all in the age of 17 or 18,

271
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,759
and just start to fall in love.

272
00:24:34,759 --> 00:24:35,559
Don't talk nonsense.

273
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:37,240
I'm not.

274
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,000
Fine, you don't admit it.

275
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,319
Then let me ask you,

276
00:24:41,839 --> 00:24:42,640
why

277
00:24:42,759 --> 00:24:43,720
you are normal
with others

278
00:24:44,799 --> 00:24:45,680
these days,

279
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:47,240
but just feel awkward

280
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,160
with me?

281
00:24:48,799 --> 00:24:49,680
You're not normal.

282
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,559
Fine.

283
00:24:59,759 --> 00:25:00,960
I'll tell you.

284
00:25:02,319 --> 00:25:03,599
Look, someone wrote you a love letter.

285
00:25:03,599 --> 00:25:04,440
It's not a big deal.

286
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:07,920
A love letter?

287
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:11,920
Go away.

288
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:14,039
Zhao Yi, what are you doing?

289
00:25:14,039 --> 00:25:15,680
Just tell me.

290
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,720
