It's not in vain

580
00:38:30,519 --> 00:38:31,840
that I've worked so many nights.

581
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:37,440
Enough.

582
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,760
Congratulations, Chuan.

583
00:38:49,159 --> 00:38:50,000
I'm going to dry my hair.

584
00:39:08,519 --> 00:39:09,400
We can eat now.

585
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,719
I accidentally fell asleep.

586
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:33,920
It seems that you're too tired.

587
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,559
Wash your hands and have dinner.

588
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:37,679
Go to bed early tonight.

589
00:40:02,599 --> 00:40:04,760
I bought it on my way to the mall last night.

590
00:40:07,639 --> 00:40:08,559
For me?

591
00:40:10,599 --> 00:40:11,719
Didn't you forget to bring a hair tie?

592
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:14,599
Yeah.

593
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,280
This is too expensive.

594
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:23,440
You can spend money on it,

595
00:40:24,079 --> 00:40:25,239
but I can't?

596
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:30,199
I have a legitimate reason

597
00:40:30,199 --> 00:40:31,280
to give you a gift.

598
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:33,960
What's your reason?

599
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:46,480
Then...

600
00:40:48,719 --> 00:40:50,559
Happy New Year in advance.

601
00:40:52,639 --> 00:40:53,360
Is it reasonable enough?

602
00:40:59,719 --> 00:41:00,239
Thank you.

603
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,159
Put it on first.

604
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:06,280
It's more convenient to eat.

605
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,119
Hello, here's your express delivery.

606
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:36,000
Hello, here's your express delivery.

607
00:42:36,559 --> 00:42:38,559
Express delivery? Are you sure it's for me?

608
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:42,960
Is it Xu Huaisong?

609
00:42:43,440 --> 00:42:43,840
Yes.

610
00:42:44,599 --> 00:42:45,840
This is a same-city express delivery.

611
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:46,639
The client requested
it must be delivered

612
00:42:47,119 --> 00:42:47,960
tonight,

613
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:50,000
and you must personally sign for it.

614
00:42:50,360 --> 00:42:51,800
It's a surprise for you.

615
00:42:52,519 --> 00:42:53,320
What surprise?

616
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:55,920
Surprise?

617
00:43:27,480 --> 00:43:28,599
Miss Ruan, please.

618
00:43:29,079 --> 00:43:29,760
This house

619
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,400
is a rare large apartment

620
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:32,880
within the second ring road.

621
00:43:34,679 --> 00:43:36,159
The furniture and appliances

622
00:43:36,360 --> 00:43:38,159
are all top international brands,

623
00:43:38,400 --> 00:43:39,599
and well-maintained.

624
00:43:39,840 --> 00:43:40,800
Each of the three bedrooms

625
00:43:41,039 --> 00:43:42,440
has its own bathroom.

626
00:43:42,679 --> 00:43:44,039
The value for money is unbeatable.

627
00:43:45,440 --> 00:43:46,679
How much is the rent?

628
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:47,880
4,000 yuan.

629
00:43:48,639 --> 00:43:49,159
What?

630
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:53,719
If you think

631
00:43:53,719 --> 00:43:55,039
the price is too high,

632
00:43:55,039 --> 00:43:55,840
we can negotiate.

633
00:43:58,039 --> 00:43:59,000
Negotiate?

634
00:43:59,760 --> 00:44:00,599
As far as I know,
houses of the same size and type

635
00:44:01,519 --> 00:44:03,039
in this community

636
00:44:03,400 --> 00:44:04,719
rent for around

637
00:44:04,719 --> 00:44:05,719
18,000 yuan.

638
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:10,559
The landlord of this house

639
00:44:10,559 --> 00:44:12,159
is abroad for a long time.

640
00:44:12,360 --> 00:44:13,519
If these appliances

641
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:15,239
are not used for a long time,

642
00:44:15,239 --> 00:44:15,920
they will be easy to break down.

643
00:44:16,199 --> 00:44:17,679
So the tenant is like

644
00:44:17,840 --> 00:44:18,840
maintaining the house.

645
00:44:19,719 --> 00:44:20,599
That's why the price
is lower.

646
00:44:22,159 --> 00:44:22,760
I see.

647
00:44:23,519 --> 00:44:24,599
Thank you.

648
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:25,679
I'll get in touch
if I need anything.

649
00:44:28,800 --> 00:44:29,400
Miss Ruan.
Thank you.

650
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:31,079
If you have any concerns,

651
00:44:31,079 --> 00:44:32,119
just let us know.

652
00:44:32,719 --> 00:44:33,400
No worries, Miss Ruan.
Take your time.

653
00:44:34,719 --> 00:44:35,519
Bro,

654
00:44:36,320 --> 00:44:37,079
the agent said

655
00:44:37,199 --> 00:44:38,639
the client didn't like any of them.

656
00:44:40,079 --> 00:44:41,119
What kind of houses did you pick?

657
00:44:44,079 --> 00:44:44,679
Bro, look,

658
00:44:45,440 --> 00:44:47,159
whether it's the landscaping, renovation,

659
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,119
height, lighting, or ventilation,

660
00:44:49,119 --> 00:44:49,880
I carefully selected

661
00:44:49,880 --> 00:44:50,920
every single one

662
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:52,239
according to your instructions.
They're all

663
00:44:54,039 --> 00:44:54,599
pretty good.

664
00:44:54,800 --> 00:44:56,440
So, how much did you quote?

665
00:44:56,920 --> 00:44:57,599
4,000.

666
00:44:58,480 --> 00:44:59,639
I really don't get it.

667
00:44:59,960 --> 00:45:00,840
How can someone

668
00:45:00,840 --> 00:45:02,360
not be tempted by this price?

669
00:45:02,719 --> 00:45:03,719
What's wrong with people these days?

670
00:45:04,079 --> 00:45:05,199
Do they treat money like dirt?

671
00:45:07,679 --> 00:45:10,440
You must have worked really hard.

672
00:45:11,320 --> 00:45:12,119
Not at all, not at all.

673
00:45:12,119 --> 00:45:13,159
Bro, it's my duty.

674
00:45:14,039 --> 00:45:14,679
I should do it.
